    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who prioritizes reliability over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few minor scratches along the passenger side. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, though it remains functional and comfortable. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly serviced, though it may soon require some routine maintenance like new brake pads. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that would serve as a great commuter or a first vehicle for someone looking for a dependable ride at a reasonable price.",
