    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior is in great shape, though it does show some light surface scratches and minor road wear consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronics and climate controls functioning perfectly. Mechanically, the car is solid, offering a smooth ride and reliable performance for its next owner. It\u2019s an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle that has been cared for properly.",
