      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for your next great project? This car is a fantastic opportunity for anyone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to life! While it currently needs some significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it\u2019s a diamond in the rough waiting for the right owner to restore its former glory. Grab this bargain today and turn it into your own custom masterpiece!",
